title: [Bug]: bash: ./teams-for-linux-2.0.12-arm64.AppImage: cannot execute binary file: Exec format error
body:
### Can you reproduce this bug in the website/PWA?

No

### Describe the bug

Attempting to launch the AppImage results in nothing. Attempting to launch from the commandline gives the subject error.

### What package are you using?

AppImage

### Version

2.0.12

### Reproduction steps

```markdown
1. Download AppImage
2. Set executable flag
3. Double-click or run from command line.
...
```

### Expected Behavior

```markdown
1. App should open
2.
3.
...
```

### Debug

```markdown
teams-for-linux --webDebug --logConfig='{}'
```

### Additional context

_No response_
